Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.90,0:00:07.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,突然就從下午開始停課了什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.73,0:00:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說起來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.86,0:00:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遙今天費了大量心思做的便當
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.32,0:00:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是為了大兔做的？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.91,0:00:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不…不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.32,0:00:18.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是…因為偶爾起得早了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.00,0:00:21.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遙？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.83,0:00:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的…不是那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.97,0:00:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大兔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.05,0:00:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有吃了便當呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.44,0:00:48.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大兔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.15,0:00:49.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.44,0:00:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第三次了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.11,0:00:55.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.79,0:01:02.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25}魔術　\h\h\h\h\N{\r}毒？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.16,0:01:03.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.25,0:01:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和我所使用的 相同的毒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.25,0:01:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25\pos(841,650)}魔術
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.58,0:01:08.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和希梅亞相同…的…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.42,0:01:09.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.63,0:01:10.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25}吸血鬼\N{\r}是上古魔法師吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.25,0:01:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.84,0:01:15.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.97,0:01:16.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.80,0:01:18.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之 我覺得那很棘手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.80,0:01:19.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.22,0:01:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以死的次數到恢復為止
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.81,0:01:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有十分多鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.73,0:01:27.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,必須小心儘量不要死了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.06,0:01:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.40,0:01:30.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回學生會室吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.86,0:01:31.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.94,0:01:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發生了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.19,0:01:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然去問令人火大的會長大人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.20,0:01:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很打擊人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.75,0:01:53.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鏘鏘～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.63,0:01:59.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 我不是說鏘鏘了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.59,0:02:01.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼無視啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.10,0:02:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能破除所有力量的凶劍
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.81,0:02:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.98,0:02:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唯一能讓那把劍的力量失效的對手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.94,0:02:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是做為天魔使者的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.99,0:02:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天使們
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.74,0:02:22.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 美雷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.62,0:02:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.91,0:02:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道「天魔」嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.04,0:02:26.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.97,0:02:42.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果哥哥不自量力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.89,0:02:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要豢養那女的的話 就給一個忠告吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.35,0:02:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定要小心 來自月的侵蝕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.10,0:02:52.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.69,0:02:54.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日向這小子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.73,0:02:57.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說我不可能豢養希梅亞？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.28,0:02:59.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就來證明那是錯的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.74,0:03:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要親吻
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.03,0:03:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要親吻
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.08,0:03:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.00,0:03:12.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,詛咒解除啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.63,0:03:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,精神百倍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.00,0:03:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安度的米雷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.25,0:03:18.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敵人來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.01,0:03:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的天魔的同夥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.10,0:03:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無視了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.10,0:03:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好大膽量
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.15,0:03:36.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼 好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.52,0:03:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,月光 快點快點～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.23,0:03:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來是人可以活動的空間呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.49,0:03:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.57,0:03:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來是對面的邀請呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.22,0:05:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,月光那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.55,0:05:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這種時候 到哪裡去偷懶了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.05,0:05:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像有什麼東西在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.93,0:05:33.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.85,0:05:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像很危險呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.94,0:05:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.73,0:05:37.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是敵人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.11,0:05:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 已經被殺了三次了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.82,0:05:45.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以很明顯有敵意呐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.62,0:05:55.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.96,0:05:58.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不從那裡上樓的話 就沒法去學生會室了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.83,0:06:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們戰鬥的話 能贏嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.21,0:06:02.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.84,0:06:04.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希梅亞？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.51,0:06:07.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說…希梅亞 你在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.72,0:06:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希梅亞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.82,0:06:26.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不…不可以過來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.29,0:06:35.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.74,0:06:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第四次了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.38,0:06:44.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希梅亞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.21,0:06:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以過來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.88,0:06:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別過來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.01,0:06:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.22,0:06:49.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要看…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.13,0:06:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.30,0:06:53.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在來救你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.81,0:06:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.68,0:06:56.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.14,0:06:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.39,0:07:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.85,0:07:01.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.40,0:07:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想要我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.82,0:07:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希梅亞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.86,0:07:11.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易…才見到大兔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.91,0:07:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不想和大兔再一次…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.70,0:07:16.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再一次…分開…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.70,0:07:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…馬上救你出來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.75,0:07:19.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大兔…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.88,0:07:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.31,0:07:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種感覺嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.63,0:07:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希梅亞？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.06,0:07:43.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,賽托希梅亞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.73,0:07:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你愛上的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.56,0:07:47.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是這麼無聊的人類啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.94,0:07:50.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了這種渣滓
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.99,0:07:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就拋棄我了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.37,0:07:56.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.66,0:07:58.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發生了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.54,0:08:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和你 沒有關係！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.38,0:08:06.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你 不是希梅亞！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.25,0:08:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大兔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.67,0:08:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笨～蛋～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.68,0:08:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了 這樣一來…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.10,0:08:20.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是死了第六次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.18,0:08:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再殺一次的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.64,0:08:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙就不會再復活
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.56,0:08:27.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.44,0:08:30.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.57,0:08:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巴爾思庫拉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.81,0:09:02.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要走了 巴爾思庫拉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.60,0:09:08.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你喜歡那傢伙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.90,0:09:11.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.57,0:09:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼對那種傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.87,0:09:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是個人類啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.91,0:09:22.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是愚蠢…又渺小的人類啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.37,0:09:23.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.29,0:09:25.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.42,0:09:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至少比我們…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.17,0:09:30.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不骯髒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.09,0:09:31.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你才不骯髒…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.30,0:09:34.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真溫柔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.42,0:09:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你總是很溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.51,0:09:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.22,0:09:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看看這個骯髒的身體吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.27,0:09:48.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個骯髒到極點的身體…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.90,0:09:50.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看看吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.49,0:09:56.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,漫長的 漫長的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.32,0:09:59.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在漫無止境的孤獨中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.91,0:10:01.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,變得極度黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.49,0:10:02.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,污穢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.53,0:10:04.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被侵蝕成這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.46,0:10:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隨著月亮的陰晴圓缺
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.21,0:10:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,詛咒也日益漸深
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.93,0:10:20.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經 太痛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.18,0:10:22.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太寂寞了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.06,0:10:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.52,0:10:26.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不得不結束這一切
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.10,0:10:27.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巴爾思庫拉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.23,0:10:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想要陪伴你 到最後一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.94,0:10:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起度過最後一刻的對象
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.49,0:10:39.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想自己選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.78,0:10:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個對象
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.28,0:10:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是那個人類嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.20,0:10:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.50,0:10:50.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了那樣的人類 你打算死嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.67,0:10:52.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.84,0:10:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.38,0:10:56.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.55,0:10:57.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是這樣認為的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.22,0:11:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 巴爾思庫拉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.34,0:11:02.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我對他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.85,0:11:05.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對大兔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.89,0:11:07.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的愛得很深哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.89,0:11:08.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是連…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.27,0:11:13.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個永恆的身體
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.48,0:11:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,消失不見也在所不惜的程度
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.86,0:11:19.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希梅亞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.99,0:11:21.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被那個叫巴爾思庫拉什麼的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.03,0:11:23.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搶走身體了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.49,0:11:26.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼做才好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.08,0:11:29.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎樣才能把那傢伙從身體裡驅趕出去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.29,0:11:31.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在開玩笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.08,0:11:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玷污搶奪她的心的不就是你嗎 人類
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.89,0:11:50.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她是屬於我的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.89,0:11:52.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美麗的賽托希梅亞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.52,0:11:53.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是只屬於我的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.06,0:11:57.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我要帶走她
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.86,0:11:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到你無法觸及的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.87,0:12:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帶到你絕對無法觸及 只有我和她的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.12,0:12:09.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.46,0:12:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大兔…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.58,0:12:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.79,0:12:20.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我壓制住他的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.34,0:12:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.55,0:12:24.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.47,0:12:25.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希梅亞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.14,0:12:28.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行…又…壓制不住…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.60,0:12:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點…快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.31,0:12:32.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在逃了的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.60,0:12:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不就會像九年前那樣 你被這傢伙帶走了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.44,0:12:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我沒理由一個人逃走…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.56,0:12:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了 大兔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.40,0:12:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽我的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.40,0:12:43.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒辦法再保護你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.53,0:12:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想你死
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.08,0:12:49.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你死了的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.58,0:12:50.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.16,0:12:50.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希梅亞？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.42,0:12:57.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.79,0:12:59.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定會救你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.42,0:13:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 可惡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.17,0:13:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我算什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.55,0:13:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼總是什麼都做不了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.22,0:13:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,賽托希梅亞…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.68,0:13:09.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了那樣的渣滓 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.89,0:13:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太礙眼了 去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.61,0:13:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這點程度 還死不了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.50,0:13:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大兔…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.92,0:13:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 遙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.42,0:13:43.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學生會長找我去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.42,0:13:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說是突然有工作
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.30,0:13:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你的便當
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.59,0:13:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,待會兒會吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.55,0:13:50.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.30,0:13:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是學生會的工作的話 也沒辦法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.39,0:13:54.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對…對…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.18,0:13:56.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好想見你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.94,0:13:58.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好想見你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.69,0:14:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,確實 平凡也不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.98,0:14:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.97,0:14:36.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遙？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.81,0:14:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 大兔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.98,0:14:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在方便嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.06,0:14:43.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊…不…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.61,0:14:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稍微有點…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.82,0:14:45.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大兔？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.32,0:14:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.15,0:14:47.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出什麼事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.28,0:14:50.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事都沒有…不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.24,0:14:53.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不說這個了 有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.41,0:14:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是算了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.91,0:14:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好像很忙的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.54,0:15:01.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.33,0:15:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呐 大兔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.63,0:15:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不知道發生了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.38,0:15:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別太蠻幹哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.67,0:15:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還記得嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.92,0:15:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想 在練空手道的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.13,0:15:14.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是好幾次對抗年長的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.51,0:15:16.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直到全身到處是傷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.60,0:15:21.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 沒逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.27,0:15:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.11,0:15:25.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 大…兔…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.17,0:15:45.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 不逃了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.25,0:15:49.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稍微想起來 我是怎樣的傢伙了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.88,0:15:51.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你小子搞什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.55,0:15:55.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我啊…完全不懂得放棄的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.43,0:15:57.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之前也是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.76,0:15:58.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,掙扎再掙扎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.39,0:16:01.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最後總是能獲得最終的勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.06,0:16:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最後…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.23,0:16:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.40,0:16:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.45,0:16:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希梅亞在那裡的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.83,0:16:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.78,0:16:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定會讓她恢復的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.45,0:16:22.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最早一次死開始 已經過了十五分鐘嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.62,0:16:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但那又能怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.71,0:16:27.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都不做到的現實
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.17,0:16:29.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又沒有改變
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.88,0:16:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽…聽得到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.01,0:16:33.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽得到的吧 希梅亞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.55,0:16:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.47,0:16:37.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,留下你 自己逃跑是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.47,0:16:39.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.64,0:16:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣即使活下來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.93,0:16:42.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有你的存在 不就沒有意義了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.64,0:16:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.81,0:16:46.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就殺你七次
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.90,0:16:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.32,0:16:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,變成這種狀況
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.82,0:16:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巧妙的解決方式一個也想不出
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.78,0:16:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是任何時候 一直…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.58,0:16:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陪伴在希梅亞身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.79,0:17:05.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該和她在一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.96,0:17:06.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.29,0:17:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就憑無知 無能 無力的你這種傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.46,0:17:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還要保護她？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.34,0:17:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.47,0:17:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25}　　　　　　魔術\N{\r}被希梅亞施下毒的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.09,0:17:18.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發過誓的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.10,0:17:20.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發過誓了啊 希梅亞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.51,0:17:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發誓「無論生死 永遠在一起」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.94,0:17:29.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鐵大兔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.65,0:17:31.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對不會原諒你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.32,0:17:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,醜陋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.36,0:17:36.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只配在地上爬的區區螻蟻之徒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.49,0:17:38.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卻被她愛著的你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.66,0:17:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希梅亞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.16,0:17:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.41,0:17:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 這樣子你這混蛋死五次了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.42,0:17:49.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還剩下一條命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.79,0:17:51.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那之後就沒了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.67,0:17:53.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那樣足夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.88,0:17:56.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呐 希梅亞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.93,0:17:57.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.80,0:18:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明是將她毀成這樣的罪魁禍首
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.89,0:18:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她因為愛你而瘋狂 選擇了死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.02,0:18:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為你的緣故
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.23,0:18:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她已經幾乎沒剩多少時間能活了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.69,0:18:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.15,0:18:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保護她 救她？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.24,0:18:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別笑死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.45,0:18:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別笑死人了 別笑死人了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.32,0:18:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,殺死她的不就是你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.79,0:18:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了你這樣的渣滓 她…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.75,0:18:29.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大…兔…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.96,0:18:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大兔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.80,0:18:36.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為…為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.97,0:18:40.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希梅亞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.59,0:18:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這條命 為你而留
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.89,0:18:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我對希梅亞…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.73,0:18:50.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我對大兔…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.54,0:19:16.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我愛你 大兔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.39,0:19:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…是為了保護你而創造出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.48,0:19:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.35,0:19:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你無法保護我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.06,0:19:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能夠保護我的 只有大兔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.48,0:19:38.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,創造我的是你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.90,0:19:41.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了讓你不再寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.70,0:19:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我被創造出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.45,0:19:43.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.41,0:19:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我還是寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.16,0:19:49.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的話 無法填補我心中的空虛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.46,0:19:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能填補我內心空虛的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.46,0:19:54.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有大兔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.50,0:19:57.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能找到我的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.50,0:19:58.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有大兔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.59,0:20:01.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天魔要來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.47,0:20:06.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天魔要來侵犯已經失去力量的你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.43,0:20:09.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那樣一切都完了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.72,0:20:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,失去力量的你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.27,0:20:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有防備他們的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.23,0:20:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我的幫助…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.52,0:20:15.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.82,0:20:18.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 巴爾思庫拉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.19,0:20:23.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…能在大兔身邊歡笑的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.53,0:20:25.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.33,0:20:27.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就足夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.83,0:20:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.42,0:20:34.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巴爾思庫拉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.88,0:20:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,永別了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.26,0:20:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,賽托希梅亞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.35,0:20:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,賽托希梅亞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.22,0:20:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要忘記
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.89,0:20:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能保護你的 不是鐵大兔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.94,0:20:58.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而是我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.90,0:21:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大…兔…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.32,0:21:07.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希梅亞？是希梅亞吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.49,0:21:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.46,0:21:17.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呐 大兔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.38,0:21:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.97,0:21:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.72,0:21:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.18,0:21:30.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用你的溫暖
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.14,0:21:34.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來滿足 我的身體
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.56,0:21:41.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 大兔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.90,0:21:46.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點來抱我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.58,0:23:23.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 她已經醒了？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.92,0:23:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.63,0:23:26.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一切都按計劃進行？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.84,0:23:27.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.17,0:23:31.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上古魔女 賽托希梅亞
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.30,0:23:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,必須阻止她完成秘法《幸福》啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.56,0:23:37.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.64,0:23:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是專門為此製造出來的 這點…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.40,0:23:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.11,0:23:44.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.69,0:23:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真是個聽話的好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.86,0:23:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了 退下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.66,0:23:55.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,繼續 進行監視
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.03,0:23:56.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.87,0:24:01.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我好痛苦 大兔
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.37,0:24:03.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.67,0:24:09.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…為什麼在這種地方
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.59,0:24:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼人類那麼讓人厭惡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.43,0:24:15.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大兔以外的人全都死了的話
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.64,0:24:17.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就可以和大兔過二人世界了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.10,0:24:20.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乾脆用魔法讓人類滅亡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.43,0:24:22.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但那樣做了的話 大兔會生氣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.98,0:24:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過大兔生氣的樣子也喜歡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.23,0:24:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 想著大兔的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.43,0:24:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,心裡就跳個不停
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.40,0:24:31.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是滅了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.45,0:24:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為想和大兔兩人單獨相處嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.14,0:24:35.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就滅了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.65,0:24:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下等的人類們 做好覺悟吧
